14
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:50,670
♪Saling menemani sepanjang waktu♪

15
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:52,870
♪Ternyata teman baru
seperti teman lama♪

16
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:55,700
♪Pertemanan bisa terjalin
